      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "刘杭燕在绣阁自思自想，想起了梵王宫年少的儿郎。我二人见面在佛堂以上，亚赛个当年小潘郎。多亏了花妈妈计生心上，命华云巧改扮美貌娘行。将身儿坐至在牙床以上，等候了花轿到再作主张。",
      "text_length": 87
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00004",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "嫂子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00005",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "将身儿来至在绣阁内，见了姑娘说分明。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00006",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "小姑娘，花轿到了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00007",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "待我去迎。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00008",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "你不是病了么？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00009",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "我的病么，早已好了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
