        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "你家哥哥，与人家打架未回。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00025",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "嫂嫂将新人藏在奴的房中，去至上房，将新人身契文约，偷将出来，明日放她逃走，岂不是一了之备？",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00026",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "好一个一了之备。我要去了。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00027",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "嫂子下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00028",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "与我走出去罢！去了他头上的盖巾。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00029",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "噌吓，妙吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00030",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "有华云在洞房用目观看，小姑娘只生得亚赛天仙。但愿得苍天爷心随我愿，我与她作一对并头双莲。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00031",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "刘杭燕在洞房偷眼观看，观看他只生得盖世无双。明知道小华云男扮女来，女孩家羞答答难以开言。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00032",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "嫂嫂请来见礼。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00033",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "还礼。小生华……",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00034",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "“华”什么？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00035",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "小生华云。只因那日梵王宫，相见一面，观见小姐见爱。今日前来，与小姐做伴来了吓！",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00036",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "我有心将终身大事，托付于你。到后来，不要忘了奴的好意。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00037",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "若要忘了小姑娘的好意，死在乱箭之下。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00038",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "言语太重了。你我拜什么为媒？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00039",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "现有桌台为媒。请吓！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00040",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "请吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00041",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "拜过了桌台为媒证，我与你做夫妻永不离分。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00042",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "来来来咱夫妻上床安眠，好夫妻上牙床永不离分。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00043",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘杭燕、华云同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00044",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "咱二人清早起才把床下，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00045",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘杭燕、华云同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00046",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "怎不叫人喜在心！将身坐在绣阁内，再对小姐说分明。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00047",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "小生告辞。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00048",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "且慢。你要逃走了，叫奴怎样舍得你吓？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00049",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "小姑娘不必如此，你可有什么心爱之物赠我，后来还有相逢之日吓。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00050",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "我说是华郎、华郎吓，你等着。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00051",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "叫华郎你不必泪流满面，听为妻把话对你言。我这里开开箱将鞋取出，临行时赠与你凤头花鞋。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00052",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "嫂子上。丫鬟、花妈妈同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00053",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "行走来在绣阁外，叫声丫鬟叩门庭。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00054",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "丫鬟前去叩门。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00055",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花妈妈"
      ],
      "text": "慢着，她不会，待我去叩开门来。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00056",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "花妈妈叩门。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00057",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "来了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00058",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花妈妈"
      ],
      "text": "小姑娘你那病可好了？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00059",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘杭燕"
      ],
      "text": "我那病么，早已好了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00060",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花妈妈"
      ],
      "text": "我晓得你早已好了。那么一来，就好了。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00061",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "苦吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00062",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "你也不用哭了，拿这五十两银子，你走去罢！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00063",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花妈妈"
      ],
      "text": "想夫人待你这样仁义，还不谢了夫人！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00064",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "拜夫人！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00065",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花妈妈"
      ],
      "text": "哽！先拜后跪下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00066",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "哦哦是了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00067",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "华云"
      ],
      "text": "拜夫人你的恩情好，这件事倒叫我面目发烧。走上前来双膝跪倒，",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00068",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "嫂子"
      ],
      "text": "叫丫鬟把门开，说是他再也不回来。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00069",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "嫂子下。华云下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01006012_e00070",
      "play_id": "01006012",
      "scene_id": "01006012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
